definition.value: An alkylamine having isobutyl as the alkyl group. It has been isolated from Sambucus nigra (Elderberry).
A 7,8-dihydropterin having a diphosphomethyl substituent at the 6-position.
A 2-oxo monocarboxylic acid that is pyruvic acid in which one of the methyl hydrogens is substituted by a 4-hydroxyphenyl group.
